	<h1 class="title">「这世界」伊朗总统来了，意大利的裸体像们都穿上了衣服</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/4695/small/4695.jpg?1418026962" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">孙若空 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-01-28 12:58:59 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/21433/medium/21433.jpg?1453954051" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


